high_descs: Turn around to walk into the bedroom and face the bed.
Pick up the lettuce from the bed.
Turn right and walk right to exit the room and walk up to the floor lamp and turn left to reach the fridge.
Cool the lettuce in the fridge and take out the lettuce.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Put the lettuce in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold lettuce in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and head through the doorway, then take left immediately and go to the foot of the bed.
Pick up the lettuce from the foot of the bed.
Leave the room the way you came in, go straight ahead to the wall, then turn left and go towards the fridge in the kitchen area.
Place the lettuce into the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out.
Go to the microwave to the left of the fridge.
Place the lettuce in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Cool a head of Lettuce in a fridge and place it in a Microwave.

high_descs: Turn around to head to the bedroom on the left to reach the bed.
Pick up the lettuce from the bed.
Turn around and turn left to reach the fridge in the kitchen.
Cool the lettuce in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left to reach the microwave.
Put the lettuce in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled lettuce in the microwave.
